      <title>印度驳斥花旗集团就业报告 称存在数据缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/india-refutes-citigroup-s-employment-report-alleging-data-gaps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府驳斥了花旗集团的一份报告，该报告称即使印度经济以每年 7% 的速度增长，该国也将难以创造足够的就业机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/india-refutes-citigroup-s-employment-report-alleging-data-gaps</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登告诉立法者、捐助者是时候结束对候选人资格的反抗了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/biden-tells-lawmakers-he-s-running-time-to-end-talk-of-swap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登试图平息民主党内围绕他的总统竞选活动的内讧，他说他决心继续参加竞选，并挑战反对者停止有关将他从选票中剔除的言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/biden-tells-lawmakers-he-s-running-time-to-end-talk-of-swap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 13:10:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国财政大臣不打算改变英国央行储备利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/uk-chancellor-has-no-plans-to-change-interest-on-boe-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新任财政大臣表示，她没有计划改变英格兰银行储备金的利息支付方式，而英国央行在危机时期的债券购买计划给政府带来的损失正受到越来越多的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/uk-chancellor-has-no-plans-to-change-interest-on-boe-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 12:20:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度准备从俄罗斯获得长期铀供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/india-poised-to-secure-long-term-uranium-supply-from-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情高级官员表示，俄罗斯和印度很可能就南部泰米尔纳德邦即将上线的核电站的长期铀供应协议达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/india-poised-to-secure-long-term-uranium-supply-from-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 12:06:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞、萨尔维尼将加入奥尔班的新极右翼欧盟联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/le-pen-salvini-to-join-orban-s-new-far-right-eu-alliance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 新生的欧盟联盟周一影响力进一步提升，以法国候选人玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 和意大利候选人马泰奥·萨尔维尼 (Matteo Salvini) 为首的两大极右翼政党同意加入该联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/le-pen-salvini-to-join-orban-s-new-far-right-eu-alliance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 11:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党推迟批准陆上风电项目，以加快建设速度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/labour-clawbacks-approval-for-onshore-wind-to-speed-up-building</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯表示，英国新工党政府将寻求通过取消导致地方团体拖延项目的繁文缛节来加快陆上风电项目的审批流程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/labour-clawbacks-approval-for-onshore-wind-to-speed-up-building</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:07:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织将考虑降低大额借款人罚款的方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/imf-to-discuss-options-for-lowering-penalties-on-big-borrowers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一些国家担心由于利率上升导致成本变得不合理之后，国际货币基金组织将讨论对其向最大借款人收取的费用进行审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/imf-to-discuss-options-for-lowering-penalties-on-big-borrowers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基谴责俄罗斯炮火袭击基辅医院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/kyiv-comes-under-attack-in-missile-strike-across-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基谴责俄罗斯发射的导弹袭击，这次袭击导致基辅一家儿童医院部分受损，这是乌克兰全国范围内一系列袭击的一部分，造成至少 31 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/kyiv-comes-under-attack-in-missile-strike-across-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:54:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡僵局风险，法国股市涨幅缩减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于立法选举产生分裂的议会且没有明显多数，投资者评估了政治僵局带来的风险，法国股市回吐了早前大部分涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/french-stocks-decline-after-surprise-leftist-win-banks-weaken</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京接待莫迪，称赞与印度竞争对手中国的关系“史上最佳”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/putin-hosts-modi-after-hailing-best-in-history-ties-with-india-rival-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在莫斯科加深与新德里竞争对手中国的联系之际，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪周一抵达俄罗斯，这是他五年来首次访问俄罗斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/putin-hosts-modi-after-hailing-best-in-history-ties-with-india-rival-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
